  "prompt": "I'm new to Quora. What does it mean when someone says they are following me?",
  "response": "Welcome to Quora! On this platform, when someone says they are following you, it means they have chosen to subscribe to your activity on Quora. When someone follows you, they will see your answers, posts, and other contributions in their feed. It's a way for users to keep up with the content you're sharing and possibly engage with it by commenting, upvoting, or sharing. Enjoy your time on Quora and happy sharing!",
